<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l21">ʒum Altmanſteın </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_166_r1l22"><expan>L<ex>ıeber</ex></expan> Hanns als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>ıben</ex></expan> habt von der <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> leẅt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> wıe den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l23">niht fugſam ſey vor vns ʒu <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıgeln</expan> daʒ wır getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l24"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu ıſt das geſcheft daʒ dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l25">fraw getan hat mıt des Reıchs gerıcht bey vns <expan>ʒugang<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l26">des gerıchts <expan>Jnſ<ex>igel</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıgelt</expan> <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> . als des gerıchts form vnd <expan>gewonh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l27">bey vns ıſt / Deẅcht <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> leẅt . daʒ ſıe <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l28"><expan>gelaſſen<ex>en</ex></expan> hab <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu den <expan>leẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> den das geſchıkt ıſt . ıht <expan>ʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
